**Usage:**
1. Detection skill creates this file when implementation reaches threshold (e.g., 3+ interactive components)
2. OR triggered pre-ship by shipkit-pre-ship-check
3. `/shipkit-ux-audit` reads this queue
4. Skill audits for missing UX patterns (loading states, errors, accessibility, feedback)
5. Creates checklist in `.shipkit/references/ux/ux-checklist.md`
6. Marks items complete in this queue

**Example:**

```markdown
